---
import SketchEditor from '../components/SketchEditor.astro';
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>p5 v2 @ lgm 2026</title>
    <style>
      body { margin: 2rem; font-family: sans-serif; background: #111; color: #eee; }
      h1 { margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
      p  { margin-bottom: 2rem; color: #aaa; }
      a.enter {
        display: inline-block;
        margin-top: 2rem;
        padding: 0.5rem 1.2rem;
        border: 1px solid #eee;
        color: #eee;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 4px;
      }
      a.enter:hover { background: #eee; color: #111; }
      .contributors {
        margin-top: 3rem;
        opacity: 0.75;
      }
      .contributors img {
        max-width: 100%;
        border-radius: 6px;
      }
      .contributors p {
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        color: #666;
        margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>p5 v2 @ lgm 2026</h1>
    <p>What is p5? Drawing with code, JavaScript, access and inclusion, all-contributors</p>
    <p>history of 2.0;  2.0+ artist series; PF mission, p5.js focuson inlcusion and access; and strands specifically</p>
    <SketchEditor />
    <a class="enter" href="sketch">demo →</a>
    <div class="contributors">
      <p>p5.js contributors</p>
      <img src=`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/fetched-assets/contributors.png` alt="p5.js contributors" />
    </div>
  </body>
</html>